---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout
  title="Abhishekh Ojha | Full Stack Developer"
  description="Learn more about Abhishekh Ojha (also known as Abhishek Ojha), a Full Stack Developer and AI Engineer building scalable web applications."
  url="https://www.abhishekhojha.com/abhishekh-ojha"
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24 min-h-screen text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 tracking-tight">
        Abhishekh Ojha
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Hello! I am <strong>Abhishekh Ojha</strong> (often spelled as <strong>Abhishek Ojha</strong>), a passionate Full Stack Developer and AI Automation Expert based in India. I specialize in building highly scalable, responsive web applications and integrating advanced AI capabilities into modern digital solutions.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        With extensive experience in the MERN stack and Next.js ecosystem, I focus on delivering seamless user experiences and robust backend architectures. My journey in software engineering has allowed me to work on diverse projects, from high-performance e-commerce platforms to sophisticated AI-driven tools that streamline business operations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        My Expertise
      </h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg">
        <li><strong>Frontend Development:</strong> React, Next.js, Astro, Tailwind CSS</li>
        <li><strong>Backend Development:</strong> Node.js, Express, MongoDB, PostgreSQL</li>
        <li><strong>AI & Automation:</strong> LLM Integrations, LangChain, Custom AI Workflows</li>
        <li><strong>DevOps & Deployment:</strong> Docker, AWS, Vercel, CI/CD Pipelines</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6">
        As <strong>Abhishek Ojha</strong>, I constantly strive to stay at the forefront of technology, embracing new frameworks and methodologies to solve complex problems efficiently. Whether it's architecting a new application from scratch or optimizing an existing system for better performance and SEO, I bring dedication and a detail-oriented approach to every project.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
        <a href="/" class="text-[var(--brand-dark)] dark:text-[var(--brand-light)] font-semibold hover:underline">
          &larr; Back to Homepage
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
